yo mitrāya varuṇāyāvidhajjano.anarvāṇaṃ taṃ pari pātoaṃhaso dāśvāṃsaṃ
martamaṃhasaḥ \| tamaryamābhi rakṣaty ṛjūyantamanu vratam \|  
